Package: superadmixture
Title: Inference of Population Structure by Super-admixture Framework  
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Danfeng", family = "Chen", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "danfengc@princeton.edu", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4489-0485")), person(given = "John D.", family = "Storey", role = c("aut"), email = "jstorey@princeton.edu", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5992-402X")))
Maintainer: Danfeng Chen <danfengc@princton.edu>
Description: This package provides functions for inference of population coancestry and simulating genotypes according to the super-admixture framework.  It also has functions for conducting the structured Hardy-Weinberg equilibrium test and estimating admixture proportions using the ALStructure algorithm.
